title: Did God Use Evolution? -  - Dr Werner Gitt epub/mobi
description:
Did God Use Evolution?: Observations from a Scientist of Faith -  - Dr Werner Gitt epub/mobi

Drawing from a variety of topics - and showing their relation to one another in solving this question, author Werner Gitt reveals that evolution is bad science. Written for the layman, but with a scientific slant, this compelling book devastates Darwinian arguments for the origin of our universe and planet.
